text.div: Selected diagnoses for Female, White or Caucasian patients aged 45-64 seen as either outpatients or inpatients at Johns Hopkins Hospital, JHCP, and Bayview between 3/1/2016 and 3/1/2018 having a diagnosis of diabetes recorded on the problem list or as an encounter diagnosis.
